<%- if @subscription.needs_payment_info? -%>
<p>
Your <%= Saas::Config.app_name  %> trial period will be ending soon. If you'd
like to continue to use your <%= Saas::Config.app_name  %> account, please log
in to your account and enter your billing information. Otherwise,
your account will be disabled when your trial period ends.
</p>
<%- else -%>
<p>
Your <%= Saas::Config.app_name  %> trial period will be ending soon. If your account remains
open beyond the trial expiration date, your payment method on file will
be charged <%= number_to_currency(@subscription.amount) %> monthly.  
</p>
<%- end -%>

<p>
Billing Information:
<a href='http://www.hipscan.com/account'>http://www.hipscan.com/account</a>
</p>

<p>
Trial Expiration Date:
<%= @subscription.next_renewal_at.strftime('%m-%d-%Y').squeeze(' ') %>
</p>

<p>
If you have any questions, please email <%= Saas::Config.from_email %>.
</p>